The method involves finding adversarial examples, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the robustness of neural networks, which is a common topic in computer security (cs.CR) and neural networks (cs.NE). Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.CR, and cs.NE.
